Want to learn how to protect your family and everything you’ve worked so hard for? Join me tonight at 6:30 PM at the University Community Center in Irvine for an informative estate planning session.

Can’t make it? No worries! I’ll be at the Yorba Linda Community Center on March 20, 2025, at 6:30 PM.

Don’t miss this chance to get your questions answered and take control of your future! See you there!
